---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="flex flex-col place-content-center gap-3 xl:flex-row">
      <div class="mr-10 ml-10 flex flex-col items-center gap-3">
        <h1
          class="w-75 justify-start text-center text-5xl uppercase xl:w-150 xl:text-8xl"
        >
          instant day
        </h1>

        <p class="w-72 text-center text-black xl:text-xl">
          Join us in honouring Instant Day, where every click captures a memory
          and every print tells a story worth keeping
        </p>
        <p
          class="mt-3 mb-3 w-35 border-t border-b p-1.5 text-center text-black xl:w-45 xl:text-xl"
        >
          18. October 2025
        </p>
        <div class="mt-5 flex flex-col items-center">
          <img
            class="max-xl:h-16 max-xl:w-60"
            src="/images/countdown.png"
            alt=""
          />
        </div>
        <div class="mt-10 flex flex-row justify-center divide-x-1">
          <p
            class="pt-3 pr-5 pb-3 text-center text-[8.91px] font-bold xl:text-xl"
          >
            SAVE THE DATE
          </p>
          <p
            class="pt-3 pr-5 pb-3 pl-5 text-center text-[8.91px] font-bold text-black xl:text-xl"
          >
            SHARE YOUR INSTANT
          </p>
          <p
            class="pt-3 pb-3 pl-5 text-center text-[8.91px] font-bold text-black xl:text-xl"
          >
            2025 CONTRIBUTIONS
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="relative mt-15 h-60 w-56 place-self-center">
        <div>
          <img
            class="absolute h-50 w-40 rotate-[8.19deg] border"
            src=""
            alt=""
          />
        </div>
        <div>
          <img
            class="absolute top-25 left-20 h-50 w-40 rotate-[-23.47deg] border"
            src=""
            alt=""
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="home-info-what mt-25 h-[513px] place-content-center">
    <div class="flex max-h-175 flex-row gap-7 bg-[#2F2F2F] xl:flex-row-reverse">
      <div class="m-5 flex flex-col gap-5 place-self-center">
        <div>
          <h1 class="text-2xl text-white">What is Instant Day?</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="">
          <p class="w-48 text-xs font-light text-white xl:w-200 xl:text-xl">
            October 18 is Instant Day - a day all about celebrating instant
            photography. So get out your Polaroid, Instax or whatever instant
            photography camera you are using, and show us your instants. Instant
            Day isn’t really a photo competition, it’s more a homage to good old
            analogue, instant photography - everybody who participates are
            winners:-) But: We do have a nice prize for one lucky instant
            photographer!
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <section class="home-info-why max-xl:mt-10 xl:mt-50">
      <div class="">
        <div>
          <div
            class="mr-11 ml-11 flex flex-col place-items-center gap-4 xl:w-220 xl:place-self-center xl:text-xl"
          >
            <h2>WHY INSTANT PHOTOGRAPHY?</h2>
            <p>
              Instant photography began in the 1940s, when Edwin Land invented
              it after his daughter asked to see photos right away. Polaroid
              became a cultural icon, booming in the 70s and 80s before nearly
              vanishing in the digital age. Today, as people seek analogue,
              offline experiences, instant photography is making a
              comeback—offering a tactile, life-affirming way to capture
              memories. Let’s celebrate life and keep making them.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="home-info-how">
      <div>
        <div class="place-start mt-20 mr-11 ml-11">
          <h2>HOW TO PARTICIPATE</h2>
          <p class="">
            So, got an instant photo ready for the public? In order to take part
            in Instant Day:
          </p>
          <div class="gap mt-10 flex flex-col gap-5 xl:flex-row">
            <div>
              <h2>1.</h2>
              <p class="text-[12px] xl:text-lg">
                Take a photo of your instant with your smartphone (or scan it
                for max. quality) - the file should be between 2 - 10 MB, in
                jpg/jpeg or webp format.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h2>2.</h2>
              <p class="text-[12px] xl:text-lg">
                Upload your photo and credentials on [link til din “share your
                instants” side]
              </p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h2>3.</h2>
              <p class="text-[12px] xl:text-lg">
                By joining, you agree to our [terms and conditions]. In short:
                you must be 18+, have consent from anyone in your photo, and
                allow us to exhibit and promote your instant.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h2>4.</h2>
              <p class="text-[12px] xl:text-lg">
                You can make up to 5 submissions - go through step 1-3 for each
                submission;-)
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="home-former-gallery mt-20 bg-[#2F2F2F]">
      <div>
        <div>
          <h1 class="place-self-center pt-10 text-white">
            Former participants has uploaded
          </h1>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="p-15">
        <div
          class="flex flex-col gap-5 self-start justify-self-center border border-white"
        >
          <div class="relative -top-10 h-10 w-30 self-center bg-[#2F2F2F]">
          </div>
          <div class="relative top-510 h-10 w-30 self-center bg-[#2F2F2F]">
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-10 place-self-center pr-15 pb-15 pl-15">
            <img class="h-72 w-60 border" src="" alt="1" />
            <img class="h-72 w-60 border" src="" alt="2" />
            <img class="h-72 w-60 border" src="" alt="3" />
            <img class="h-72 w-60 border" src="" alt="4" />
            <img class="h-72 w-60 border" src="" alt="5" />
            <img class="h-72 w-60 border" src="" alt="6" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="home-inspiration"></section>
  </section>

  <style>
    .home-info-what img {
    }
  </style>
</Layout>
